title: Prison Stories: The Funny, The Bad & The Ugly
description:
This week, Tasia and Camo tell some funny (and not so funny) stories from their respective times behind bars. Tasia details waking up to 20-30 naked women yelling at her and how people would often steal the guards food. On the other side, Tasia also discusses the truly dark side of prison, including the time a small fight ended up in someone dying. Camo also discusses his 2 trips to jail and all the fights he's been in, and being ready for a future fight.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
